{
  "2234910": {
    "name": "废土机器人：返祖",
    "steam_appid": 2234910,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/9be6ef6326249047279a199f4dd46e3d.poster.avif?t=1759021361\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/9be6ef6326249047279a199f4dd46e3d.webm?t=1759021361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/9be6ef6326249047279a199f4dd46e3d.mp4?t=1759021361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《废土机器人：返祖》</strong>是一款融合了Roguelike元素的卡牌生存游戏。您可以体验到以下<strong>核心玩法循环</strong>：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索：</strong>闯荡随机生成的广阔的废土世界，收集赖以生存的资源，以及遭遇各类变异生物和仿生人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>资源：</strong>通过简单的拖曳堆叠，完成资源的全部行动——组合、交互与回收。例如，将“机油”拖到“电脑板碎片”上，将会生成“芯片沙拉”。越大胆尝试，越会有意料之外的收获。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>研究：</strong>收集蓝图，解锁新科技，打造出符合你的生存哲学的物品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战斗：</strong>夜幕降临时，你需要抵御黑暗中想置你于死地的生物围攻。它们会在每个夜晚卷土重来，做好准备！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏背景</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/c32c26d4d3fd17e392a0f1b1be7e722d.poster.avif?t=1759021361\" width=1170 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/c32c26d4d3fd17e392a0f1b1be7e722d.webm?t=1759021361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/c32c26d4d3fd17e392a0f1b1be7e722d.mp4?t=1759021361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt; 新纪元198年，『大毁灭』已经过去了198年。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt; 你从落满灰尘的角落醒来... 金属关节发出生涩的摩擦声，光学传感器亮起微弱红光...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt; 透过坍塌的屋顶，你看见铅灰色的天空不断落下辐射尘，远处传来变异乌鸦的嘶鸣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt; 一条指令在你的处理单元里闪烁了起来——“去吧，找到<strong>『最后的所在』</strong>”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt; 你需要马上动身，赶往那『最后的所在』，那里希望尚存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt; 在此之前，尽一切可能，生存下去吧。但要在这里活下去，你需要在一些见不得光的领域成为专家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索废土</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>随机地图：</strong>每局游戏都拥有独一无二、由程序生成的随机地图。『大毁灭』后的废土大陆，已经不复往日生机，这里遍布大量可探索的废墟和资源。当然，你会遭遇暗中观察的变异生物和仿生人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>潜行机制：</strong>提高你的潜行值，然后加上亿点点运气，幸运的你可能会成功潜入目的地，获得超大份的奖励。但是如果潜行失败，那就做好接受惩罚的准备！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/48c8719c07e5254c1a60a053a3d793fe.poster.avif?t=1759021361\" width=512 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/48c8719c07e5254c1a60a053a3d793fe.webm?t=1759021361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/48c8719c07e5254c1a60a053a3d793fe.mp4?t=1759021361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经营资源</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>操作：</strong>通过简单的卡牌交互方式——拖曳堆叠，完成资源的全部行动——组合、交互与回收。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>组合：</strong>生存的关键在于不断尝试。不管你获得的什么资源，都大可尝试下不同的组合。“卷纸”配上“电脑板碎片”，可以获取大受欢迎的“雪茄”，“木材”扔进“火堆”，则可以制造有用的材料“木炭”。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/aaed664e17d4d89bf2053d2ff5c8c039.poster.avif?t=1759021361\" width=612 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/aaed664e17d4d89bf2053d2ff5c8c039.webm?t=1759021361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/aaed664e17d4d89bf2053d2ff5c8c039.mp4?t=1759021361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>科技研究</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>蓝图：</strong>你虽孑然一身，白手起家，但随着探索的深入，收集到的蓝图越多，解锁的新科技就越多。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>科技：</strong>资源，工具，武器，防具，改造等多种类别，数百个科技蓝图，相信你能找到适合自己的生存之道。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/6cf71a0d316ba597df4f4bcc7b332e8f.poster.avif?t=1759021361\" width=512 height=470 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/6cf71a0d316ba597df4f4bcc7b332e8f.webm?t=1759021361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/6cf71a0d316ba597df4f4bcc7b332e8f.mp4?t=1759021361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>抵御围攻</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>和平阶段：</strong>敌对生物会尾随你但是按兵不动。你得想办法在这期间多积攒一些物资，或者多消灭一些敌人？你自己作出选择。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>敌袭阶段：</strong>夜幕降临时，你将要面对一波集中的进攻，而且你无法反击。当你熬过去，便会进入新一轮和平阶段<strong>。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/f2569b3922d5d320189dafc9dd35ddba.poster.avif?t=1759021361\" width=1170 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/f2569b3922d5d320189dafc9dd35ddba.webm?t=1759021361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/f2569b3922d5d320189dafc9dd35ddba.mp4?t=1759021361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>终极目标</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存：</strong>生存，生存，生存永远是你的第一目标，悉心管理好你的时间和资源，在保守和激进中作出权衡。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>使命：</strong>你追寻那神秘女人的『<strong>天启之语</strong>』，在辐射云将整个世界吞噬之前，前往『<strong>最后的所在</strong>』，把生命重新带回这个世界。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/7fb123272ccb3ba7a010a42aa3c92104.poster.avif?t=1759021361\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/7fb123272ccb3ba7a010a42aa3c92104.webm?t=1759021361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234910/extras/7fb123272ccb3ba7a010a42aa3c92104.mp4?t=1759021361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>开发路线</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>v0.9 (当前版本)：</strong>核心玩法已就绪，包含10小时游玩内容。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>v1.0 (开发中)：</strong>优化性能，丰富故事，调整数值，增加更多物品与怪物，30小时游戏游玩内容。（正式上线版本）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>v1.1 (计划中)：</strong>增加主角随从</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>v1.2 (计划中)：</strong>增加主角多职业选择</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>v1.3 (计划中)：</strong>增加Mod扩展支持</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加入我们的开发之旅</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款由个人开发者全力打造的游戏，它目前正处于<strong>内部测试</strong>阶段，这意味着它已经有可玩的核心内容，但远未完美。我们坚信，与玩家社区的紧密合作是成功的关键。我们真诚地邀请您成为<strong>游戏的共同创造者</strong>，您的建议和反馈将直接帮助我们决定未来的优化方向和新增内容。欢迎加入我们的Steam讨论区，告诉我们您的想法。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您喜欢『<strong>辐射</strong>』<strong>、</strong>『<strong>饥荒</strong>』<strong>、</strong>『<strong>堆叠大陆</strong>』<strong>、</strong>『<strong>卡牌生存</strong>』<strong>或者</strong>『<strong>末日启示录</strong>』的游戏体验，那么我们的游戏可能也会非常适合您。在本作中，我们尽量剥离经典生存游戏中让人头痛的<span class=\"bb_strike\">复杂性和压力</span>，并将其与慢节奏的卡牌游戏结合。希望这款游戏会为你带来新的体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏使用开源的Godot引擎开发，我们从中得到了许多快乐，希望更多的开发者也能加入Godot社区。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家交流&amp;问题反馈QQ群：</strong>669745372</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>反馈邮箱：</strong><a href=\"mailto:farther2009@outlook.com\">farther2009@outlook.com</a></p></li></ul>",
